### Performance & Detection Fixes (2025-12-26) ✅

**Side Profile Detection Bug Fix:**
- Fixed orientation inversion in `looksmaxx-app/src/lib/sideProfileDetection.ts:199`
- Changed `faceOnLeft ? 'right' : 'left'` to `faceOnLeft ? 'left' : 'right'`
- Landmarks no longer "stick to the left side"

**Image Downsampling for Performance:**
- `looksmaxx-app/src/lib/faceDetectionService.ts` - Downsamples to 640px max
- `looksmaxx-app/src/lib/sideProfileDetection.ts` - Downsamples to 480px max
- 4-9x faster detection for high-resolution images

**Leaderboard UI Enhancement:**
- `looksmaxx-app/src/components/results/tabs/LeaderboardTab.tsx` - Shows photos, strengths, improvements
- `looksmaxx-api/app/routers/leaderboard.py` - Added top_strengths/top_improvements to API

